metadata.name: I'm Phoenix!
metadata.description:
I'm Phoenix, with wings of fire,
A warrior's spirit, fierce and dire.
My fiery essence, my heart and soul,
A burning passion, my only goal.

I soar above, with flames aglow,
A warrior's path, the only road I know.
With every beat of my heart, I rise higher,
A fighter's strength, an unquenchable fire.
